                </figure>
                <div class="section-intro animated wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="1s">
                    <header class="entry-header">
                    		                        <span class="entry-subtitle">
	                            Standing Together	                        </span>
                                                	                        <h2 class="entry-title">
	                           When We Come Together We Can Do Anything	                        </h2>
                                            </header>
                                        	<a class="button animated wow fadeInUp" data-wow-duration="0.5s" href="https://paullottfordelegate.com/paul-lott-in-the-media/">Paul Lott In the Media</a>
                	                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>    <section class="event-section default-padding">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-wrap">
	                        	
		                <div class="section-intro animated wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1s">
		                	 
			                    <header class="entry-header">
                                                                            <span class="entry-subtitle">
                                            OUR EVENTS                                        </span>
                                    			                        <h2 class="entry-title">
			                            Upcoming campaign near by you			                        </h2>
			                    </header>
			                    <div class="section-description">
			                    	
<p>Show your support and come out to meet Paul Lott and hear what he will do when elected as your 28th District Delegate. We will address serious issues and have a little fun while doing it. Your show of support will go a long way in creating the momentum we need to win and take back Virginia. </p>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>New events are announced frequently so check back and add them to your calendar.</p>
			                    </div>
